[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    11[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    12[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Recipe 11.10 is the chapter's tenth and capstone recipe in Conversational AI / Virtual Assistants and the first recipe in the chapter (and indeed in the cookbook so far) to combine IRB-as-active-participant-in-product-development as architectural primitive (not phase 2), per-trial-IRB-approved-content-corpus-as-the-only-source-of-trial-specific-recruitment-language as load-bearing safety primitive, per-trial isolation as structural rather than advisory architectural posture, deterministic-eligibility-evaluation-engine with per-criterion clinical-leadership ownership and version history and IRB-review evidence as architectural primitive, vulnerable-populations-aware identity model with explicit 45 CFR 46 Subparts B/C/D handling, trial-state-and-trial-amendment-tracking as separately-governed runtime primitive, recruitment-funnel instrumentation as multi-cohort regulatory-and-scientific obligation aligned with FDA diversity-action-plan reporting, coordinator-handoff orchestration as production scope co-designed with the coordinator team rather than as engineering afterthought, research-data-as-distinct-record-class with research-grade retention distinct from clinical-care-PHI handling, and the chapter-pattern set of cross-cutting commitments inherited from 11.1 through 11.9 (input safety screening with continuous emergency screening, identity verification, tool-use orchestration with strict citation grounding, output safety screening, audit logging, scope discipline across adjacent chapter-11 pathways, prompt-injection defense, graceful degradation, citation grounding, crisis-pathway routing).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    13[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    14[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The opening Maria vignette earns its position as the chapter's clearest single articulation of the recruitment-funnel-as-structural-failure-mode primitive. The 52-year-old in central Texas with insulin-resistant T2DM, the endocrinologist's printout with three trial study identifiers and a 90-mile-distant phone number, the office hours conflicting with Maria's work shift, the voicemail that took four days to call back, the forty-minute thirty-five-question call where most answers were "I'm not sure, I'd have to check my chart", the ten-day silence, the discovery that trial three closed enrollment three weeks earlier (which had not been reflected on the printout), and the three-hours-on-the-phone and two-weeks-elapsed and meaningful-frustration accumulation to learn she might qualify for one trial pending further review are operationally accurate and recipe-distinct. The "if you talk to clinical research coordinators about their daily work, this is a recognizable arc" pivot earns its position as the recipe's clearest articulation of the recruitment-funnel-as-known-and-documented-structural-failure-mode primitive.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    15[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    16[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The Technology section is the chapter's strongest pedagogy on IRB-grounded-conversational-recruitment-as-citation-bound-corpus-retrieval-with-deterministic-eligibility-evaluation-and-coordinator-handoff and executes at the right grain. The "Why Clinical-Trial Recruitment Has Resisted Digital Tools" subsection grounds the structural-failure-mode (form-based-prescreens-do-not-handle-the-conversation-and-call-centers-are-finite-and-the-coordinator-supply-is-thinnest-where-the-trials-fail-most) in specific architectural diagnoses. The "What a Clinical Trial Recruitment Conversationalist Actually Does" subsection's eleven-task-surface decomposition (entry from a referral source with appropriate context, trial-specific context loading and disclosure, patient-question-handling using IRB-approved FAQ retrieval, conversational eligibility prescreen, prescreen-result delivery to the patient, coordinator-handoff orchestration, equity-and-representativeness instrumentation, sensitive-topic handling within recruitment scope, continuous emergency screening across every utterance, out-of-scope routing, per-conversation audit and IRB-grade record retention) is correctly granular and recipe-distinct. The "Why a Generic LLM Cannot Run a Clinical Trial Recruitment Conversationalist" subsection's fourteen-property enumeration (no theory of IRB-approved recruitment language; no theory of eligibility-criteria depth; hallucinates trial information when grounding is weak; no theory of staying within scope; no theory of assent versus consent versus surrogate-decision-maker; no theory of vulnerable populations under 45 CFR 46 Subparts B/C/D; clinical-decision-rule arithmetic problems; no theory of trial-status state; no theory of what to do when the patient is in distress; no theory of relationship to the existing care team; compliance implications specific to recruitment data; no theory of representativeness monitoring; no theory of coordinator