[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     95[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   1. **Per-record-class retention reconciliation.** The recruitment-decision-record journal, the conversation-state store, the conversation-archive, the prescreen store, the representativeness store, the tool-call ledger, the IRB-approved-content corpus, the eligibility-rule library, the FAQ corpus, the consent record, the trial-state store, the trial-amendment audit log, and the coordinator-handoff queue-state may have different retention floors. The longitudinal-conversation-state store may need active-trial-life-plus-trial-closeout-period retention. The recruitment-decision-record journal may need the longest-of-HIPAA-research-provisions-plus-45-CFR-46-plus-FDA-IND-or-IDE-record-retention-where-applicable-plus-state-specific-medical-record-retention-plus-litigation-hold floor. The conversation archive may need the recruitment-decision-record-journal floor.
